<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta
        name="viewport"
        content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"
    >

    <title>xdayoungx Hub</title>

    <link
        rel="preconnect"
        href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com"
    >

    <link
        rel="stylesheet"
        href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.7.2/css/all.min.css"
    >

    <style>
        :root {
            --bg: #0d1117;
            --card: #161b22;
            --border: #30363d;
            --text: #f0f6fc;
            --muted: #8b949e;
            --green: #3fb950;
            --green-hover: #2ea043;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: Inter, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: #0d1117;
            color: var(--text);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="header">

                <div class="logo">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-code"></i>
                </div>

                <div class="title">
                    xdayoungx Hub
                    <span class="online-dot"></span>
                </div>

                <div class="subtitle">
                    Grow a Garden 2 스크립트를 사용하려면 아래 버튼을 눌러 복사하세요.
                    <br>
                    현재 서비스가 정상적으로 운영되고 있습니다.
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
